## **Sub-task 1: Raise ServiceNow Change Request and Carry Out End-to-End Process**

**Sub-task Title:**  
Raise ServiceNow CR and Complete End-to-End Process for Prod VPC Endpoint Upgrade

**Sub-task Description:**  
- Raise ServiceNow Change Request (CHG) for Production VPC endpoint upgrades.  
- Prepare the runbook for the upgrade steps and rollback procedures.  
- Perform upgrade in coordination with the AWS implementation team.  
- Capture detailed test evidence before and after the upgrade.  
- Conduct post-implementation validation to ensure VPC endpoints are functioning correctly.  
- Update related documentation (runbook, evidence, endpoint list).  
- Close ServiceNow CR post successful validation and evidence submission.

**Sub-task Comment (for Jira):**  
> Raised and completed ServiceNow CR (CHG35514839) for Production VPC endpoint upgrades.  
> Post-validation confirmed successful functioning of all 11 endpoints.  
> Documents uploaded:  
> - **Runbook:** `Runbook_XBSD_SDS_111597_vpc_endpoints_V2.xlsx`  
> - **Evidence:** `VPC Endpoint Upgrade - Evidence.docx`  
> - **Endpoint List:** `vpc-endpoint-remediation_all.xlsx`  
> - **Procedure:** `ServiceNow Change Request Procedure.docx`

