## **Sub-task 2: Production Environment VPC Endpoints Upgrade**

**Sub-task Title:**  
Upgrade 11 VPC Endpoints in Production Environment

**Sub-task Description:**  
- Coordinate with the AWS implementation team to carry out the VPC endpoint upgrade for 11 Production endpoints.  
- Execute the upgrade as per the approved ServiceNow Change Request.  
- Perform pre- and post-validation checks on all upgraded endpoints.  
- Ensure zero downtime or issues post-upgrade.  
- Document and update the endpoint list accordingly.

**Sub-task Comment (for Jira):**  
> Successfully upgraded 11 Production VPC endpoints to the latest version.  
> Post-upgrade validation confirmed no service impact to B2B Supplier Directory Services.  
> All upgrade evidence captured and documented.

---

## **Sub-task 3: Dev Environment VPC Endpoint Upgrade (Access Permission Issue)**

**Sub-task Title:**  
Resolve Dev Endpoint Permission Issue and Complete Upgrade

**Sub-task Description:**  
- Coordinate with the AWS administration team to resolve access permission issues for the Development VPC endpoint.  
- Once access is granted, proceed with upgrading the endpoint to the latest version.  
- Perform post-upgrade validation to ensure proper functionality.  
- Update the documentation with the final upgrade status.

**Sub-task Comment (for Jira):**  
> Coordinated with AWS administration team to resolve Dev endpoint permission issues.  
> Successfully upgraded the Development VPC endpoint post-resolution.  
> Validation completed; no issues observed.  
> Evidence added to the upgrade document.

